A pregnant woman and two doctors have been reported dead at the Malam Aminu Kano Teaching Hospital (AKTH) following a suspected outbreak of Lassa fever in the state. Others who were said to be infected with the virus have been taken to the intensive care unit of the hospital. It was gathered that the pregnant woman who hails from Bauchi State is suspected to be a carrier. She was said to have died after undergoing a caesarean section about 20 days ago at the hospital. However, the Director, Public Health, Kano State Ministry of Health, Dr Imam Wada Bello, on Tuesday disclosed that a female doctor on housemanship that died recently assisted in the caesarean section carried out by the consultant who is now dead also. ALSO READ: BREAKING: Gov Ortom wins as Supreme Court dismisses Jime’s appeal BREAKING: Gov Ortom wins as Supreme Court dismisses… [BREAKING] Adamawa guber: Supreme Court affirms… Rainfall: NIMET predicts near-normal onset, normal cessation… BREAKING: Former Supreme Court judge, Justice Abubakar Wali,… He further disclosed that a sample has been taken to Lagos for analysis adding that results are expected tomorrow. However, the information officer of the state ministry of health, Alhaji Sama’ila Gwammaja, also explained that the case is a suspected case and the blood sample had already been taken for analysis. Gwammaja said, “the result is expected tomorrow (Wednesday) hopefully by 2 pm. We will call a press conference to let the public know about the situation.” A statement from the Nigeria Medical Association (NMA) in Kano said the state chapter is “dismayed by the recent happenings, death of colleagues as a result of contact with suspected case of Lassa fever.” The statement noted that it is very urgent and imperative that the authorities should direct all machinery for effective control of the public health dangers to act promptly. It also called on the public to use all the appropriate and necessary measures to curb and control the spread of this infectious disease. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE